==Description==
The '''Rare Bone''' is a type of [[Underground|Underground Item]].

==Details==
The '''Rare Bone''' has a value of 3 [[Diamonds]] {{Diamonds}} when sold. It can also be traded in Daily Deals.

==Mine Layout==
The Rare Bone appears in the Underground as a 6x3 sized object.<br><br>
[[File:RareBoneMine.png|100px]]

==Acquisition==
Rare Bones can be found in the [[Underground]], as [[Rare Hold Items]] from [[File:Cubone.png|30px]] Cubone, [[File:Marowak.png|30px]] Marowak, [[File:Dwebble.png|30px]] Dwebble, and [[File:Crustle.png|30px]] Crustle, and as Loot in [[Dungeons]].

